      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 74.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 74.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>奈何以死懼之？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>to what purpose is it to (try to) frighten them with death?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-074__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-074</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 74.3 - 老子 74.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 74.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>若使民常畏死，而為奇者，吾得執而殺之，孰敢？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>If the people were always in awe of death, and I could always seize those who do wrong, and put them to death, who would dare to do wrong?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
