      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 74.8 - 老子 74.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 74.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫代司殺者殺，是謂代大匠斲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He who would inflict death in the room of him who so presides over it may be described as hewing wood instead of a great carpenter.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
