      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 74.10 - 老子 74.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 74.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫代大匠斲者，希有不傷其手矣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Seldom is it that he who undertakes the hewing, instead of the great carpenter, does not cut his own hands!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
